{"id":"mobilemusic-6aa.1","title":"Create adaptive root view with sidebar/tab switching","description":"Rewrite ContentView.swift to use @Environment(\\.horizontalSizeClass). Regular width (iPad): NavigationSplitView with sidebar containing Channels, Favorites, Providers, Settings sections. Compact width (iPhone): keep existing TabView. Both paths share the same underlying views.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:35:22.956215-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc","updated_at":"2026-02-25T10:35:22.956215-06:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"mobilemusic-6aa.1","depends_on_id":"mobilemusic-6aa","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:35:22.956958-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc"}]}
