{"id":"mobilemusic-hdb","title":"Show channel icons alongside names in CarPlay channel lists","description":"Channel lists in the CarPlay interface should display the channel's icon/logo next to the channel name, similar to how they appear in the iPhone UI. For example: [ICON] Radio: Sirius XM Chill. Use the channel's logoURL to fetch and display the image in CPListItem.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-24T13:10:01.668976-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc","updated_at":"2026-02-24T13:23:34.71876-06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-24T13:23:34.71876-06:00","close_reason":"Closed","labels":["carplay","enhancement","ui"]}
