{"id":"mobilemusic-ke6","title":"Phase 11: Keyboard \u0026 Pointer Support","description":"iPad with Magic Keyboard and trackpad support. Add keyboard shortcuts for playback/navigation, pointer hover effects, and context menus for right-click.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:33:13.622051-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc","updated_at":"2026-02-25T10:33:13.622051-06:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"mobilemusic-ke6","depends_on_id":"mobilemusic-6aa","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:34:10.32965-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc"}]}
{"id":"mobilemusic-ke6.1","title":"Add keyboard shortcuts for playback and navigation","description":"Space = play/pause, Cmd+1-4 = switch sections (Channels/Favorites/Providers/Settings), Cmd+F = search, Cmd+N/Cmd+P = next/prev channel, Esc = dismiss sheets/modals. Use .keyboardShortcut() modifier and @FocusState for focus management.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:21.587041-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc","updated_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:21.587041-06:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"mobilemusic-ke6.1","depends_on_id":"mobilemusic-ke6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:21.587657-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc"}]}
{"id":"mobilemusic-ke6.2","title":"Add pointer hover effects","description":"Add .hoverEffect(.highlight) on channel rows, buttons, sidebar items, and other interactive elements. Ensures Magic Keyboard trackpad users get visual feedback when hovering over tappable elements.","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:26.760278-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc","updated_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:26.760278-06:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"mobilemusic-ke6.2","depends_on_id":"mobilemusic-ke6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:26.760949-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc"}]}
{"id":"mobilemusic-ke6.3","title":"Add context menus for right-click","description":"Channel rows: Play, Toggle Favorite, View EPG, Copy Stream URL. Provider rows: Edit, Delete, Reload Channels. Use .contextMenu modifier. These also enable long-press menus on iPhone as a bonus.","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:31.938091-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc","updated_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:31.938091-06:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"mobilemusic-ke6.3","depends_on_id":"mobilemusic-ke6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-25T10:36:31.938734-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc"}]}
