{"id":"mobilemusic-utw","title":"Dynamic background color for channel icons","description":"Channel icons currently display on a white background, which causes white-on-white issues for light-colored icons. The app should analyze the PNG image and pick an appropriate background color that provides good contrast, so icons are always clearly visible.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-24T12:56:17.876349-06:00","created_by":"lecaptainc","updated_at":"2026-02-24T13:08:05.652567-06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-24T13:08:05.652567-06:00","close_reason":"Closed","labels":["enhancement","ui"]}
